    Scope and Contents
The Public Administration Program Doctoral File, 1984-91 contains material pertaining to the development of a Doctoral program in Public Affairs at SSU, including concept proposals, academic program requests, and staffing proposals.  Much of the material relates to John Collins,  Assoc. Professor of Administration and Public Affairs (1978 to present) and Randy Kucera, Assoc. Professor of Public Administration, (1974 to present).  
  
